text: Ilse Martha Ries-Hotz (born 27 July 1949) is a Luxembourgian archer. Martha Ries-Hotz competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics.Ilse Martha Ries-HotzIlse Martha RIES-HOTZ == References == Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Luxembourgian archers Category:Olympians for Luxembourg
